transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling. This is John. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, hi. I received a charge on my account for the Score Blue.

Speaker 2: When I initially signed up for it, I thought it was just a one-time thing and I would not be charged unless I asked to be charged again, because I have another subscription with another company where I can turn it on and turn it off.

Speaker 1: Unfortunately, let me get you to somebody that can help you with this.
